sourcesContent: import React, { useState } from 'react' import { Collapse, Navbar, NavbarToggler, NavbarBrand, Nav, NavItem, NavLink, UncontrolledDropdown, DropdownToggle, DropdownMenu, DropdownItem, NavbarText, } from "reactstrap"; const Menu = (props) => { const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false); const toggle = () => setIsOpen(!isOpen); return ( ); } export default Menu;
